Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:43.31,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}如伊卡洛斯一般
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.59,0:08:47.94,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}那份纯真的勇气如今已不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.99,0:08:50.29,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}我们活着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:53.66,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}将那平凡的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:55.70,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}平凡无奇地度过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:09:00.36,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}怀着无数问号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:08.18,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}寻找答案 却陷入迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:15.58,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}若能得知 答案的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:22.15,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}一切将化作崭新的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:24.70,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}这阵风的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:30.39,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}定会有真实的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.47,0:09:32.30,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:34.91,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}这些泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.98,0:09:38.50,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}总有一天会干涸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:44.60,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}即使现在还很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:49.74,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}即使现在还很遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.84,0:09:53.79,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}只需微微一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:56.50,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}便能迎着清风 乱了呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:10:00.49,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)\be1}勇往直前吧
