Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.81,0:00:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,435)\fs18\b0\fsp0}（此刻 世界上只有我们两人）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,0)}（前一天）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,0)}（放学后）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.65,0:00:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.87,0:00:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果汁也喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 学园长？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我们的顾问
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.49,0:00:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园长当顾问？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.59,0:00:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的业余爱好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是津名志拓人同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于招到期待已久的新社员了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.06,0:00:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人都是从中等部时起就入社的老社员了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个社团很没人气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.37,0:01:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正相反
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.13,0:01:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太有人气所以抬高了门槛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.98,0:01:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心喜欢须方或者和子的人太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.09,0:01:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而不敢入社 怕成为众矢之的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 倒有不少准社员给我们做服装和舞台装置的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.15,0:01:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人同学也是冲着和子大人来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子大人是少爷的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.25,0:01:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能随便说这种话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫我大人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有少爷也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷就是少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子大人也是皆水大人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许婚的事也是我父母擅自决定的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.74,0:01:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 总之
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.28,0:01:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的美少年组合都到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的「夜间飞行」剧团坚如磐石啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.86,0:01:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会设计一个能够最大限度发挥两人魅力的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人的魅力？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)}（和子妄想中）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在谁也看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 须方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天之前是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.72,0:02:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.14,0:02:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个妄想十分Good
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,100)}（你怎么知道的）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.06,0:02:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时没那方面企划
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)}（你们怎么知道的）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 剧本里也会加入和子的歌的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.83,0:02:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子的梦想是当歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是小时候的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.31,0:02:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年有泳装女优来这个岛上拍照时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有星探看中她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就别提啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子的歌声一听就会让人着迷的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 别说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺负人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用隐瞒的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.20,0:02:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必感到害羞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想的确是越具体越容易实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对大家的将来都抱有很大的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜甜的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫糖汁？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.59,0:03:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 姿目·Tiger同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.15,0:03:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要来我们社看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗅觉与记忆有很深的关联
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种香味会刺激快乐的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你有没有想起什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有想起什么快乐的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快乐的…事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tiger回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的银河里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉眠着怎样的绮罗星呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用老虎黄油烤的热饼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老虎黄油的热饼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看画册
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个午后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和须方少爷并排坐着看那本画册
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 老虎黄油烤的热饼好像很好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷也说 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那让你很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的笑容好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷是皆水大人的未婚夫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果皆水巫女和拓人同学凑成双
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方少爷就自由了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能错过机会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女心想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.66,0:05:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要打倒乌贼大王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获得驶向银河世界的船只
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是萨姆开始用手中的鱼叉练习刺乌贼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了和乌贼大王作战的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 嘿 嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未经努力获得的胜利索然无味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌贼刺杀者萨姆的大名很快传遍全国
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌贼刺杀者萨姆…真有型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女一直在海边的小屋等待着萨姆的归来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 两人就同居了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是花季的少男少女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼星球好开放啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随之而来 两人有了共同的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶 我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 奶奶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上哪儿去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.25,0:06:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是扬卷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奶奶来过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店里的菠萝包我可全吃了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好吃啊 「南原」的菠萝包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我要坐车
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人都不接
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:07:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:06.40,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}遍地的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.60,0:08:11.14,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}是升空的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.44,0:08:15.95,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}数亿的生息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:20.42,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\be1}此刻 世界转世…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.18,0:08:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,街上一个人都没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好在有你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之不是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我漂到岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.39,0:10:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你救的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.07,0:10:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是哪里都打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淋湿了 换身衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座岛上没人的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去本土看看？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里不舒服？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没离开过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巫女有封印在身 就离不开岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说这是巫女的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要想离开岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非封印被破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 一旦封印被破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙的素体也会跑到岛外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些话是谁告诉你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原先关于巫女的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是进入中学后 让奶奶教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我小学时 自作主张用了驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巫女使用驯化后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会共享得到素体的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.01,0:12:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成明白许多事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 上东京当歌手是根本不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当初可没少哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.52,0:13:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的变成只有我们俩的世界了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's a pinch 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像看到个孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图腾？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我认识…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我立的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.91,0:13:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候和须方他们一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是它…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几年前刮台风时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里发生塌方 应该不见了才对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么又会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:14:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可能不是现实世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零时空间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.75,0:14:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是零时空间？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.64,0:14:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么搞的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tauburn不来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说不是零时空间…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人 真的好无忧无虑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.86,0:14:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从前就一直这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无忧无虑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:14:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口有这道印记之前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比现在封闭得多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 因为有以前的拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才有现在的拓人对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这乐观的想法很时髦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意对口喝的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化巫女素体的那个夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭了个够
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半夜肚子饿时入口的美味饭菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我忽然想到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界不是只为折磨我而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在想来也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有拓人这样的人出现在岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会动心的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:16:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种处境偶尔也不赖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人独处时才能谈的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏在这里面的回忆之类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回忆？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有能够创造风景的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台素体会根据闯入者的回忆和愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,编织出架空的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回忆和愿望？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太心软了 沉醉（Ivrogne）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是击败银河美少年的良机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成 想让她战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 看呐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人想妨碍你的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的愿望和回忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这雾是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人 得快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么认为？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台素体是幻像？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.20,0:17:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巫女应该能分辨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我和子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 那台素体是真实的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之说明这里是零时空间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则 素体不可能行动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.96,0:17:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是说 Tauburn也在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台素体如果有创造风景的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能藏起我的Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错 Tauburn就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.05,0:18:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷也常说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最珍贵的东西往往最难被察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tauburn就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别松手 和子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飒爽登场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…创造出这世界的愿望是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你独处的这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:19:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许源自我的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她无法用素体战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.75,0:20:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是个恋爱的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.99,0:20:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先暂且不论
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次你的作战似乎成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.23,0:20:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怎么样 姿目同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是贫血
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.89,0:20:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话途中突然晕倒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:20:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.91,0:21:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌贼刺客大人和少女有了怎样的秘密？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们吃了乌贼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.01,0:21:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鱼星球上 乌贼是恶魔的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不可食用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人却一起品尝了乌贼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是乌贼刺客大人 一定吃的是刺身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不可否认
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有共同的秘密 让二人的羁绊更深了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.85,0:21:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生的冒险还在继续…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.26,0:21:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说了 今早他们又有动作？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.68,0:21:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里的事 终究全都是幻觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.09,0:21:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过和子的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.23,0:21:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍旧声声可闻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:22:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.84,0:22:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左拥右抱 我碍事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.19,0:22:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡说 不是那样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.58,0:22:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 和子唱歌了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.44,0:22:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不坏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.91,0:22:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.47,0:22:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的素体
